						<description><![CDATA[
        			<h2>New Features</h2>
        			<ul>
								<li>Added an app icon</li>
								<li>Added an opening year field to locations</li>
							</ul>
							<h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
							<ul>
								<li>The inspector now shows the selected entry correctly</li>
								<li>Resorts and locations are now sorted by their opening year</li>
								<li>Fixed a bug that prevented empty locations from being deleted</li>
								<li>MAPO windows and tabs can now have their own independent selection</li>
								<li>The “New Resort” and “New Location” windows are narrower by default</li>
								<li>Fixed a bug where opening the “New Resort” or “New Location” windows would not generate a new ID</li>
								<li>The first available sidebar item is now automatically selected</li>
							</ul>
    					]]>
						</description>
